        Generates a new SNS HTTP Delegate, used to communicate over the Internet with the SNS service.
        Parameters:
        client - AmazonSnsClient - used to put messages on the wire.
        config - Necessary to configure this delegate.
        pushMessageConverter - a message converter, to ensure the message sent is of the correct format.
        realm - the realm in which this delegate exists.
        messageDispatcher - the MessageDispatcher used to redirect incoming messages to their caller.
